    </div><div class="sliderContent"><ul class="scrollerControls"><li class="previous disabled"><span>Previous</span></li><li class="next"><span>Next</span></li></ul><div class="thumbs"><div class="swiper-container"><ul class="swiper-wrapper"><li class="swiper-slide first selected"><a href="/companies/financial/kiers-share-price-fall-post-carillion-jitters-say-analysts/10029165.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/7/2/4/3103724_Kier_Marr-College_2.jpeg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="Kier marr college 2" /></a><h2 class="heading"><a href="/companies/financial/kiers-share-price-fall-post-carillion-jitters-say-analysts/10029165.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534">Kierâs share price fall: Post-Carillion âjittersâ say analysts </a></h2><p class="text">Kier reported a healthy rise in half-year profit and revenue this morning, while pointing to a positive full-year outlook.Â </p></li><li class="swiper-slide "><a href="/companies/financial/balfour-beatty-5-things-we-learned-from-its-results/10029116.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/6/1/4/3103614_Specialists-2017_Specialist-over-25_Balfour-Beatty-Ground-Engineering.jpg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="Specialists 2017 Specialist over 25 Balfour Beatty Ground Engineering" /></a><h2 class="heading"><a href="/companies/financial/balfour-beatty-5-things-we-learned-from-its-results/10029116.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534">Balfour Beatty: 5 things we learned from its results</a></h2><p class="text">Leo Quinn was notably relaxed in front of analysts today â even smiling at one point â as he unveiled the work he is doing to steer Balfour Beattyâs continued turnaround.Â </p></li><li class="swiper-slide "><a href="/companies/contractors/laing-orourke/laing-orourke-moves-projects-and-bids/10028733.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/3/4/4/3102344_Brent-Cross-Shopping-Centre_Laing-O-Rourke_Hammerson_retail_London-2.jpg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="Laing OâRourke: Moves, projects and bids_Brent Cross Shopping Centre" /></a><h2 class="heading"><a href="/companies/contractors/laing-orourke/laing-orourke-moves-projects-and-bids/10028733.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534">Laing OâRourke: Moves, projects and bids</a></h2><p class="text">As Laing OâRourkeÂ reveals its latest financial results,Â CNÂ looks back over the key appointments, departures, projects and bids from the past 12 months.</p></li><li class="swiper-slide "><a href="/companies/contractors/carillion/carillion-5-things-we-learned-from-mps-grilling/10028565.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/8/9/5/3101895_Keith-Cochrane-Emma-Mercer-Philip-Green-Richard-Howson-Carillion-select-committe-180227-2.jpg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="Keith Cochrane Emma Mercer Philip Green Richard Howson Carillion select committe 180227 2" /></a><h2 class="heading"><a href="/companies/contractors/carillion/carillion-5-things-we-learned-from-mps-grilling/10028565.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534">Carillion: 5 things we learned from MPs' grilling</a></h2><p class="text">Former Carillion bosses appeared in front of the public accounts committee to discuss lessons learned from the contractorâs collapse. Here are five things we learned.</p></li><li class="swiper-slide "><a href="/events/inspire-me-cn-campaign-launches-in-london/10028390.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/1/4/0/3101140_Inspire-Me_launch_IMG_9490.jpg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="inspire me launch img 9490" /></a><h2 class="heading">