="swiper-slide "><a href="/companies/contractors/carillion/carillion-inquiry-hearing-6-things-we-learned/10027869.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/2/1/6/3099216_Keith-Cochrane-Carillion-select-committe-180206.jpg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="Keith Cochrane Carillion select committe 180206" /></a><h2 class="heading"><a href="/companies/contractors/carillion/carillion-inquiry-hearing-6-things-we-learned/10027869.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534">Carillion inquiry hearing: 6 things we learned</a></h2><p class="text">Carillionâs former leaders have been grilled by a joint select committee of MPs. Here are some of the key revelations from the four-hour hearing.Â </p></li><li class="swiper-slide "><a href="/companies/contractors/carillion/why-did-aberdeens-bypass-hit-carillion-so-hard/10027216.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/2/1/2/3097212_CREDIT-Joshua-Davis-Photography_generic_roads-highways-maintenance-pothole.jpg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="Why did Aberdeen's bypass hit Carillion so hard?" /></a><h2 class="heading"><a href="/companies/contractors/carillion/why-did-aberdeens-bypass-hit-carillion-so-hard/10027216.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534">Why did Aberdeen's bypass hit Carillion so hard?</a></h2><p class="text">Carillion never admitted what the problem projects were that led to its Â£845m writedown in July, which began the public chain of events the led to its collapse.</p></li><li class="swiper-slide "><a href="/companies/contractors/carillion/carillion-contracts-update-on-key-projects/10027116.article?blocktitle=Explainers&amp;contentID=18534"><img src="https://www.constructionnews.co.uk/pictures/280x187/7/4/0/3096740_Airport.City.aerial.south.jpg" class="responsiveImage" data-size-1="280x187" alt="Airport city, Manchester